name: Xiast

# Xiast

Xiast is a scheduling tool made for the yearly Software Engineering project for Computer Science students at the VUB.

## Members
* **Lars Van Holsbeeke** Project Manager
* **Youssef Boudiba** Quality Assurance Leader
* **Anders Deliens** Requirements Manager
* **Adriaan Leijnse** Design Leader
* **Kwinten Pardon** Implementation Leader
* **Nils Van Geele** Configuration Manager, Database Manager, Webmaster

## Docs
The current version of the SPMP can be found [here.](https://github.com/se1-1314/xiast-docs/blob/master/management/project/SPMP_v02.pdf?raw=true) All other documentation can be found [here.](https://github.com/se1-1314/xiast-docs)
